Effective collaboration is crucial for the success of the WellnessGameHub project. The "Collaboration" directory includes folders and resources to facilitate communication and teamwork.

Contributor Guidelines: The Contributors Guidelines subfolder outlines guilines for contributors, covering coding standards issue reporting and collaborative practices. Clear guidelines streamline the contribution process and ensure consistency across diverse contributions.

Communication Logs: Transparent communication is key. The Communication Logs subfolder stores meeting notes, discussions and decisions related to the development of wellness games. This historical record helps collaborators stay informed and contributes to the overall transprency of the project.

Idea Board: The Idea Board subfolder is a space for contributors to share and discuss ideas for new wellness game projects. It serves as a dynamic space where the community can brainstorm, propose new concepts and foster innovation within the WellnessGameHub project.

